research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for the Village of San Leanna, TX, were identified primarily from the Texas Municipal League (TML) City Officials Directory and cross-referenced with the Village of San Leanna's official website and the Texas State Directory Online. Molly Quirk is listed as Mayor. Danny Villarreal is listed as Mayor Pro Tem and a Council Member. The other listed individuals serve as Council Members (also referred to as Alderpersons).

office.name: Alderperson - Council Member - Mayor Pro Tempore
